{"tid":2079263,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方在元朗YOHO Mall商場拘捕14人涉嫌非法集結","createTime":"2020-06-25T16:21:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T00:47:59.000Z","uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5f8fbebd8ca8b48ff5f7c6dcc0dfe9fa0f81177d","tid":2079263,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T16:21:33.000Z","msg":"一批市民昨日到元朗形點商場聚集和叫口號。警方表示，截至昨晚8時半，共拘捕14人，涉嫌非法集結，包括9男5女，年齡介乎14至55歲。警方指，昨日下午有人在形點商場內非法集結，破壞公共秩序，影響商場內其他市民，亦導致部分店鋪落閘，警方到場採取拘捕及驅散行動。警方譴責有示威者滋擾商戶及顧客，重申絕不容忍違法行為。<br />\n<br />\n另外，一名55歲男子在商場內，疑因拍照問題與一名54歲女子爭執，其後懷疑用手襲擊該名女子。警方以涉嫌普通襲擊拘捕這名男子。<br />\n<br />\n2020-06-26 00:01:57"},{"pid":"bebe3794b238eed397c57c4c5a0d4d63bbdac752","tid":2079263,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T16:23:02.000Z","msg":"龍J 又唔垃人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c92ca46a891fe61ab82f969b228feb679340a78e","tid":2079263,"uid":58880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T16:23:05.000Z","msg":"有冇拉到港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba4c3e2a799ee29eb282999e7260864456cb239","tid":2079263,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T16:30:11.000Z","msg":"Yoho Mall Facebook page冇人鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e19ce8cbdfd09d05e3cc7c9c4df03213df213ee","tid":2079263,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T16:31:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdc1a65ac573fa84088942c3be32928342b3c478","tid":2079263,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ba4c3e2a799ee29eb282999e7260864456cb239","tid":2079263,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T16:30:11.000Z",